human_readable: Khaled Melliti is a Tunisian football (soccer) midfielder born on May 22, 1984, in Tunis, who measures 1.80 meters tall and weighs 78 kilograms. Melliti also participated in the 2007 FIFA Club World Cup, playing 58 minutes against Urawa Red Diamonds. He later joined Istres on free transfer in July 2011.
